"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Arbitrum Bridge\\n\\n連結：\\n<https://bridge.arbitrum.io/>\\n\\n參考影片：\\n<https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wAQ63N-1X-0>\\n\\n注意及事前準備：\\nETH鏈，要趁Gas費低在進場\\n不要打除了ETH以外的進去L2\\n需要多餘的Approve還有高額的Gas費用\\n\\n費用：\\nGas大約在70-90\\nL1 -> L2   0.008 eth\\nL2 swap沒特別注意\\nL2 -> L1  0.0006 eth\\n\\n文字教學\\n1\\\\.進去之後選擇ETH鏈連上錢包\\n\\n2\\\\.打0.025 ETH進場 (4000 eth算的話)\\n\\n3\\\\.點下Deposit 大概等10-20分鐘\\n\\n4\\\\.好了之後點右上角 Add L2 network 加入Arbitrum network\\n\\n5\\\\.進去 <https://app.uniswap.org/#/swap>\\n\\n6\\\\.右上角選擇 Arbitrum network\\n\\n7\\\\.將ETH 選擇0.01 eth swap USDT (記得看一下回來gas費夠不夠在轉)\\n\\n1. 重複7的動作3次 (來回轉算一次，最後轉回ETH)\\n\\n9\\\\.回 <https://bridge.arbitrum.io/>\\n\\n10\\\\.ETH 按下\\\"↓\\\" 從L2 打回來L1，\\n\\n11\\\\.依據上面能打回來的金額，點選Withdraw\\n\\n12\\\\.假設碰到資金不足就慢慢縮小數字直到資金足夠打回 (已編輯)\",\"timestamp\":1640007288,\"title\":\"Arbitrum Bridge交互\"},\"digest\":\"pOCF1VrXE0x3NAsuCS_b6fK5pJ9Gx9DVXTW_yNqxvaI\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x6069B7868066456c012767520857f1F932CFc9B5\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"HifpDh4o_BNmDicngNsCYmwVEacxM27_4xW3WWl9xEQ\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"HDlcZyJ62DQkF51IN98M9D-c80dMbDgwb_olQ0NUGXk\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"4mMHiclF1sx8DxMnHU4O7534KFebn3A5JETnLlbWz01rkp77LJXz9ADz3M6a91RxQOy8F_3ye14rnJRQgLV8CA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x4d3c26a5abbf483d926134505d30112b97c9d0cd166a4b9b48ae6ad98903a59727a128171d6cc184c2a1fe67240710fe0b80c8f4ffc263f1127891d3be2a22cb1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"HifpDh4o_BNmDicngNsCYmwVEacxM27_4xW3WWl9xEQ\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"HDlcZyJ62DQkF51IN98M9D-c80dMbDgwb_olQ0NUGXk\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"pOCF1VrXE0x3NAsuCS_b6fK5pJ9Gx9DVXTW_yNqxvaI\"}"